      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a practical daily driver. Mechanically, it is sound and starts reliably, though the engine shows some signs of high-mileage wear and the suspension is a bit soft. The exterior has visible scratches and a few small dings, and the interior shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and carpets. It has been regularly serviced, making it a functional choice for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
