      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and rattle kits. The engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders and has had the rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance. While the chassis and interior show signs of regular use consistent with its age, the suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. This is a driver-focused machine with a focus on drivetrain performance and throttle response via its individual throttle bodies.",
      "price": 32500.0,
